.Sh NAME
.Nm lua_isnil
.Nd check whether a value is a nil, function indicator
.Bq -0, +0, -
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In lua.h
.Ft int
.Fn lua_isnil "lua_State *L" "int index"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn lua_isnil
returns 1 if the value at the given acceptable index is nil, and 0 otherwise.
.Sh RETURN VALUES
Returns 1 if the value at the given acceptable index is nil, and 0 otherwise.
